This repository contains end-to-end tests in Playwright for the OK-Notes shop.

## How To Run

1. Run all tests using terminal:
   ```
   npm run test
   ```
   or
2. in Playwright UI:
   ```
   npm run test:ui
   ```

## Reports:

1. Generate Allure report:
   ```
   npm run report:allure
   ```

More information about Playwright can find [here](https://playwright.dev/)
